window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Fourth book in the <i>New York Times</i> best-selling Indebted Series. </p> <p>\"She healed me. She broke me. I set her free. But we are in this together. We will end this together. The rules of this ancient game can't be broken.\" </p> <p>Nila Weaver no longer recognizes herself. She's left her lover, her courage, and her promise. Two debts down. Too many to go. </p> <p>Jethro Hawk no longer recognizes himself. He's embraced what he always ran from, and now faces punishment far greater than he feared. </p> <p>It's almost time. It's demanding to be paid. </p> <p>The third debt will be the ultimate test... </p>"; 
